---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SocialShare from '../components/SocialShare.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Terms of Service for CloudyUnicorn Tools. Understand the terms, guidelines, and disclaimers for using our suite of online calculators."
>
  <div class="relative min-h-[calc(100vh-16rem)] bg-background py-16 sm:py-24">
    <!-- Grid Background -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern bg-grid-fade pointer-events-none opacity-20"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-12 animate-fade-in">
      <!-- Breadcrumbs -->
      <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-mono text-neutral-500">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-neutral-600 dark:hover:text-neutral-300">Tools</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">Terms of Service</span>
      </nav>

      <!-- Page Header -->
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">
          Terms of Service
        </h1>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 text-xs sm:text-sm font-mono">
          Last Updated: June 16, 2026 &bull; Effective Immediately
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Main Content Block -->
      <div class="prose prose-neutral dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 space-y-8 leading-relaxed font-light">

        <p>
          Welcome to CloudyUnicorn Tools. The following terms of service govern your access and use of our web-based calculation service. By utilizing any of the calculators, tools, code packages, or visual content on this site, you enter into a binding agreement to adhere to these rules. Please read these terms carefully before exploring our platform.
        </p>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">1. Acceptance of terms</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing or using this digital service, you confirm that you accept these terms of service and agree to comply with them. If you do not agree to these conditions, you are not authorized to use the service and must immediately stop accessing our web platform.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">2. Description of the service</h2>
          <p>
            CloudyUnicorn Tools provides a suite of premium, client-side, online calculators—including the Age Calculator, BMI Calculator, and Calories Calculator—as a free web service. This service operates entirely in the user's web browser using JavaScript logic to ensure fast rendering and local data privacy. We reserve the right to alter, replace, or discontinue the service or any of its features at any time without prior notice or liability.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">3. Medical and Professional Disclaimer</h2>
          <div class="border-l-2 border-brand-red pl-4 py-1 text-neutral-555 italic">
            <strong>Important notice:</strong> The calculations, estimations, and guidance outputs provided by our BMI and Calories calculators are based on standardized mathematical algorithms (such as the Harris-Benedict formula, Mifflin-St Jeor equation, WHO scale, etc.). They do not constitute medical advice, clinical diagnoses, or professional nutritional programs. Always consult a qualified physician or healthcare provider before initiating diet, exercise, or health-related adjustments.
          </div>
          <p>
            Any reliance on the outputs generated by this service is solely at your own risk. The calculations represent general approximations and should not be used as a substitute for professional clinical evaluations or advice.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">4. Permitted Use and License</h2>
          <p>
            We grant you a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable license to access and use our service for personal, non-commercial purposes. When utilizing this web service, you agree not to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1.5 text-neutral-500">
            <li>Engage in automated web scraping, data extraction, or content harvesting of site files, layouts, or calculator parameters.</li>
            <li>Use the service in any way that could disable, damage, overburden, or impair our servers or network connections.</li>
            <li>Re-host, iframe, or embed the calculators into external applications or commercial products without our prior written consent.</li>
            <li>Attempt to reverse engineer, disrupt, or modify the client-side JavaScript calculations run by this service.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">5. Intellectual Property Rights</h2>
          <p>
            All custom source code, Tailwind stylesheets, layouts, branding assets, logos, and visual interfaces are the intellectual property of CloudyUnicorn. While you are free to study the open math formulations used by our scripts, reproducing the exact styling elements, branding, or website wrapper for external public distribution is strictly prohibited.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">6. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p>
            OUR SERVICE AND THE CALCULATORS ARE PROVIDED ON AN "AS IS" AND "AS AVAILABLE" BASIS, WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EITHER EXPRESS OR IMPLIED. CLOUDYUNICORN DISCLAIMS ALL WARRANTIES, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO THE ACCURACY, RELIABILITY, OR COMPLETENESS OF CALCULATOR OUTPUTS. WE DO NOT WARRANT THAT THE SERVICE WILL BE UNINTERRUPTED, SECURE, ERROR-FREE, OR FREE OF VIRUSES OR OTHER HARMFUL COMPONENTS.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            TO THE FULLEST EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, IN NO EVENT SHALL CLOUDYUNICORN BE LIABLE FOR ANY DIRECT, INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, OR CONSEQUENTIAL DAMAGES ARISING OUT OF YOUR USE OR INABILITY TO USE THE SERVICE, THE CALCULATORS, OR THE SITE CONTENT. THIS LIMITATION APPLIES REGARDLESS OF WHETHER THE ALLEGED LIABILITY IS BASED ON CONTRACT, TORT, NEGLIGENCE, STRICT LIABILITY, OR ANY OTHER LEGAL THEORY.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">8. Governing Law and Jurisdiction</h2>
          <p>
            These terms of service and any disputes arising from your use of this service shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the jurisdiction in which CloudyUnicorn operates, without regard to its conflict of law principles. You agree to submit to the personal and exclusive jurisdiction of the courts located within that territory.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">9. Modification of Terms</h2>
          <p>
            We reserve the right to revise these terms of service at any time. When we make updates, the "Last Updated" timestamp at the top of this document will change. Your continued use of the service after modifications are published represents your consent to be bound by the updated terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">10. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            If you have questions, feedback, or need clarification regarding these terms or this service, please contact us by email at <!--email_off--><a href="mailto:support@cloudyunicorn.com" class="text-neutral-905 dark:text-white hover:underline font-medium">support@cloudyunicorn.com</a><!--/email_off-->.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>

      <!-- Social Sharing Options -->
      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800">
        <SocialShare shareText="Check out the terms and guidelines for using the free CloudyUnicorn Tools calculators!" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(8px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fadeIn 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;
  }
</style>
